  "None suggested yet": "Inga förslag ännu",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Efter svaret genererar ett tyst anrop JSON. ~250–300s/meddelande.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Ett API-anrop — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Ingen profilväxling — ingen risk",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI har full kontext",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× snabbare än Separat",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Använder tokens från huvudbudgeten (~1 700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Kan minska berättelsens längd något",
