  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Kan använda annan profil/preset",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Två API-anrop — 2–3× långsammare",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s dödtid mellan anropen",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ vid 8 meddelanden — minska till 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Profilväxling kan radera meddelanden",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Bäddar in snapshot (~1.9K) om inte = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Hur många senaste meddelanden att inkludera.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Endast Separat — Tillsammans använder STs kontext.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Snabbaste. För 1-mot-1-scener (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Balanserat. För de flesta (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Bättre kontinuitet för komplexa scener (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Maximalt sammanhang men långsammare och dyrare",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Största faktorn. 8 meddelanden ~10K — fördubbling fördubblar. 3–4 minskar 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Endast Separat läge.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Antal försök vid ogiltig JSON.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. För JSON på GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Bäddar in ögonblicksbilder. Endast Separat. Trackern får alltid den föregående.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Varje snapshot +~1.9K. 0 eliminerar. 1 för kontinuitet. Över 1 sällan nyttigt.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Injiceras som osynlig kontext — auktoritativ bakgrund.",
